name: Stadium Coin
description: Welcome to the only stadium where the crowd never stops cheering and the charts never stop pumping. Stadium Coin isn’t just another meme token — it’s a full-blown sports arena of chaos, hype, and degeneracy. Whether you're here to watch Pepe score hat tricks or Doge do a backflip in a jersey, one thing’s for sure: This is where memes become champions. No sidelines. No benchwarmers. Only full-send.
